#: ../../chapter-04.rst:29
msgid "Login into the Dashboard"
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapter-04.rst:31
msgid ""
"Pressing the Dashboard button will forward you to the Dashboard login. "
"Here you must insert the password that you've already setup (see "
":ref:`set_password command option`). If you don't remember the password, "
"you have to stop the program with CTRL-C, setup a new one and run the "
"py4web again."
msgstr ""

