#: ../../chapter-04.rst:50
msgid ""
"The “Files” tab allows you to browse the folder that contains the "
"selected app and edit any file that comprises the app. If you edit a file"
" you must click on “Reload Apps” under the “Installed Applications” tab "
"for the change to take effect (except if you use *watch* with the "
":ref:`run command option`). If an app fails to load, its corresponding "
"button is displayed in red. Click on it to see the corresponding error."
msgstr ""

